🍽️ Quick Recipe Share
Quick Recipe Share is a modern and beginner-friendly recipe website designed especially for students looking for quick, affordable, and delicious meal ideas. Built with a clean dark theme, simple navigation, and responsive design, this project is perfect for showcasing basic HTML, CSS, and JavaScript skills.

📖 About the Project
This project aims to provide an easy-to-navigate platform for students and cooking beginners to:

Explore budget-friendly recipes

View delicious food images

Navigate through a smooth animated interface

Experience dark mode support

Access a mobile-responsive layout

Whether you're a college student or a busy individual, this project offers a practical solution to eat better without spending too much time or money.

🔧 Technologies Used
HTML5 – Structure of the webpage

CSS3 – Styling with support for dark mode

JavaScript – Interactivity and animations

Responsive Design – Works on mobile, tablet, and desktop

